lease will not require any code changes for most SDK installations.  Code changes would only be required if your app implemented custom experience traits or actions.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"General-Changes","type":"heading","text":"General Changes","level":3},{"anchor":"Removed","type":"heading","text":"Removed","level":4},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To simplify the public API, "},{"code":"AppcuesExperienceAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"AppcuesExperienceTrait","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" related classes and functions no longer have public visibility. There are no current use cases for extensibility that require these to be public."}]}]}]},{"anchor":"1x-to-20-Migration-Guide","type":"heading","text":"1.x to 2.0 Migration Guide","level":2},{"anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","text":"Overview","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Updating to this release will not require any code changes for most SDK installations.  Code changes would only be required if your app made anonymous calls with user properties, implemented a custom navigation delegate, or implemented custom experience traits or actions.","type":"text"}]},{"anchor":"General-Changes","type":"heading","text":"General Changes","level":3},{"anchor":"Removed","type":"heading","text":"Removed","level":4},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Properties are no longer supported for anonymous users. "},{"code":"Appcues\/anonymous(properties:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" has been superseded by "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/Appcues\/anonymous()","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". If you require properties, use "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.appcues.sdk\/documentation\/AppcuesKit\/Appcues\/identify(use